<a href="https://annasgarden.example.com/"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 0 20 10 10 0 0 0 0-20zm7.9 9h-3.4a15.6 15.6 0 0 0-1.2-5.7A8 8 0 0 1 19.9 11zM12 4.1c.9 1.1 2 3.3 2.4 6.9H9.6c.3-3.6 1.5-5.8 2.4-6.9zM8.7 5.3A15.6 15.6 0 0 0 7.5 11H4.1a8 8 0 0 1 4.6-5.7zM4.1 13h3.4c.1 2.2.6 4.1 1.2 5.7A8 8 0 0 1 4.1 13zm5.5 0h4.8c-.3 3.6-1.5 5.8-2.4 6.9-.9-1.1-2-3.3-2.4-6.9zm5.7 5.7c.6-1.6 1-3.5 1.2-5.7h3.4a8 8 0 0 1-4.6 5.7z"/></svg><span>My blog</span></a>
</nav>
