</section>
<section class="section section-custom" aria-labelledby="sec-5-h">
<h2 id="sec-5-h">Reading now</h2>
<p>Braiding Sweetgrass by Robin Wall Kimmerer.</p>
</section>
<section class="section section-gallery" aria-labelledby="sec-6-h">
<h2 id="sec-6-h">From the garden</h2>
<ul class="gallery">
<li><img src="assets/gallery-6-1.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li><img src="assets/gallery-6-2.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
</ul>
</section>
</main>
<footer>
<p>Made in Tampere &middot; Made with <a href="https://pageforge.mtclab.net" rel="noopener">pageforge</a></p>
</footer>
</div>
